- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper focuses on improving the performance of ML models and making them more user-centric, which falls under the umbrella of AI research.
- cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing): The proposed system, Zoo, supports deployment of ML models on edge and local devices, which involves distributed and parallel computing.
- cs.SE (Software Engineering): The paper discusses the construction and deployment of ML models, which involves software engineering principles and practices.
- cs.DB (Databases): The proposed system, Zoo, involves managing and processing large amounts of data, which is a key aspect of database research.
